prodNameC: 免疫特 2500 德國痲疹病毒定量免疫球蛋白G試劑
ingredientsDesc:
* Rubella Quantitative IgG Bead Pack (L2RUB12): coated with rubella antigen (stain HPV77) partially purified form infected cells.
* Rubella Quantitative IgG Reagent Wedge (L2RUBA2): 11.5 mL of a protein-based buffer. 11.5 mL of alkaline phosphatase (bovine calf intestine) conjugated to monoclonal murine anti-human IgG antibody in buffer.
* Rubella Quantitative IgG Adjustors (LRUBL, LRUBH): tow vials (Low and High), 4 mL each human serum with IgG reactive to rubella in a buffer.
    * Rubella IgG Controls (LRUBC1, LRUBC2, LRUBC3): LRUBC1:containing human serum with IgG nonreactive to rubella.
      LRUBC2, LURBC3: containing human serum with IgG reactive to rubella.
applicantAddr: 台北市南港區園區街３號８樓
efficacy: 用在IMMULITE2500分析儀體外檢驗-定量分析成人體血清的德國痲疹病毒Rubella IgG抗體，作為RUBELLA感染的輔助診斷。
